data.description: Fantastic brick home in the heart of Fayetteville!  The interior has just been repainted & is move-in ready!  Spacious floor plan with a large formal living room with a fireplace & beautiful hardwood floor. Remodeled eat-in kitchen with granite counters, updated cabinets, stainless steel appliances to include a cooktop range, wall oven & microwave & refrigerator & cork flooring. Large sunroom with tile floor is off the kitchen & is perfect for family-time. Large master suite upstairs with a sitting area with hardwood floor & remodeled bath with a large tiled shower. The master suite, guest bedroom & guest full bath located upstairs. Downstairs you'll find a den with built-in's, bedroom, full bath & laundry rm. The area downstairs would make a perfect guest/in-law suite. Located on a corner lot with fenced backyard & tiered deck. Side entry garage with storage closets.  Lots of attic storage! Call or text us directly with any questions or to schedule time to view this beautiful home - Kevin Grullon 910-257-3027 or Shawn Grullon 910-229-1100.
data.whatILove: The location/neighborhood can't be beat!!!  The downstairs den, bedroom and full bath would make a great in-law suite!
